{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be elegant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elegant Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #1a237e; /* Deep blue */\n            --secondary-color: #3f51b5; /* Lighter blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --light-text-color: #e0e0e0;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-color: #0d103a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><polygon fill=\"%233f51b5\" points=\"0,0 100,0 100,100 0,100\" opacity=\"0.1\"/></svg>');\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .services-section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.6em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .about-section {\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .about-text h2 {\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-text p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.8;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-image img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .contact-section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n\n            .hero-section h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            .hero-section p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n\n            .about-content {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n\n            .about-image {\n                margin-top: 30px;\n            }\n\n            .services-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1><i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i> Pinnacle Financial Group</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <div class=\"container hero-content\">\n            <h2>Navigate Your Financial Future With Confidence</h2>\n            <p>Expert guidance and strategic solutions for sustainable growth and wealth management.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn\">Get a Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"services-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-piggy-bank\"></i>\n                    <h3>Investment Strategies</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored investment plans designed to maximize returns and minimize risk, aligning with your unique financial goals.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-handshake\"></i>\n                    <h3>Corporate Finance</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive financial advisory for businesses, including mergers, acquisitions, and capital raising.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Risk Management</h3>\n                    <p>Proactive strategies to identify, assess, and mitigate financial risks, ensuring stability and security.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-pie\"></i>\n                    <h3>Financial Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Holistic financial planning services covering retirement, estate, and long-term wealth accumulation.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"about-section\">\n        <div class=\"container about-content\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <h2>About Us</h2>\n                <p>Pinnacle Financial Group is a premier consulting firm dedicated to providing insightful and actionable financial advice. With years of industry experience and a client-centric approach, we empower individuals and organizations to achieve their financial aspirations.</p>\n                <p>Our team of seasoned professionals is committed to transparency, integrity, and delivering exceptional value. We believe in building long-term relationships based on trust and mutual success.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"about-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/500x350/1a237e/ffffff?text=Financial+Expertise\" alt=\"Financial Expert\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"contact-section\" id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>Let's discuss how we can help you reach your financial goals.</p>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Pinnacle Financial Group. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic smooth scrolling for anchor links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}